In its instruction No. 426, the Department adopted a position somewhat in
                            opposition to the draft convention on the following points: 
                                (a)

Paragraph 1, Article I;
                                (b)

Paragraph 6, Article I;
                                (c)

Paragraph 14, Article I;
                                (d)

Paragraph 16, Article I;
                                (e)

Article II.
